OL,3,CPolice plea over Ballymena 'double
OL,4,Cmurder and suicide' horror
OL,6,FPolice have repeated an appeal for
OL,7,Finformation after the double murder of
OL,8,Fa woman and her eight-year-old
OL,9,Fdaughter in Ballymena.
OL,11,FThe woman, 39, and girl were found
OL,12,Fdead, with a 41-year-old man, at a
OL,13,Fhouse in the Co Antrim town on Monday.
OL,15,FAll three were related, and were
OL,16,Foriginally from Poland, although the
OL,17,Fgirl is understood to have been born
OL,18,Fin Northern Ireland.
OL,20,FA vigil was held in their memory in
OL,21,Fthe town on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
