PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784531890
OL,3,CPolice plea over Ballymena 'double
OL,4,Cmurder and suicide' horror
OL,6,FOn Friday a police spokesperson
OL,7,Fconfirmed that the woman and her
OL,8,Fdaughter were murdered, and appealed
OL,9,Ffor anyone with information to speak
OL,10,Fto officers.
OL,12,F"Our investigation into their murder,
OL,13,Falong with the sudden death of the 41-
OL,14,Fyear-old man, will continue," they
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"I'm keen to offer assurance that
OL,18,Fthere is no ongoing risk to the
OL,19,Fpublic, and we are not looking for
OL,20,Fanyone else in connection with our
OL,21,Finvestigation."
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@]O]yD@AOU}D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784531890
OL,3,CPolice plea over Ballymena 'double
OL,4,Cmurder and suicide' horror
OL,6,FThey added that the family and friends
OL,7,Fhave been left "both shaken and
OL,8,Fheartbroken".
OL,10,F"This absolute tragedy has saddened
OL,11,Fthe lives of so many, from loved ones
OL,12,Fto the wider community, and will be
OL,13,Ffelt for many years to come," they
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"Family members, who are left trying
OL,17,Fto come to terms with their loss, have
OL,18,Fasked for privacy at this difficult
OL,19,Ftime."
OL,26,@oD@POUpD@LO]rD@AOUuD@]O]xD@AOU{D@FO]
